long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
**New Featureï¼šNo OpenAi or ChatGPT account needï¼**

TikGPT  is a free AI-powered listing optimizer that helps Tiktok   sellers optimize listing to improve Tiktok   search ranking. 
With the help of TikGPT , you will never need to search for Tiktok   tips or templates for your listings. Just one click, you can get some better listing choices by ChatGPT OpenAI. 

ğŸš€ Features
â€’ Optimize title of Tiktok   listing
â€’ Optimize description of Tiktok   listing
â€’ Keywords finder and Keyword suggestion
â€’ Copy optimized listing content with one click
â€’ Export optimized listing content as .doc

ğŸš€ How to use
1. Optimize title
    a. Go to listing page of the product
    b. Open the TikGPT  and select Title Generator
    c. Search and pick keywords
    d. Click Generate Title button and get suggestion.
2. Optimize description
    a. Go to listing page of the product
    b. Open the TikGPT  and select Description Generator
    c. Search and select keywords, and set parameters.
    d. Click Generate Description and get suggestion.

ğŸš€ How it works
TikGPT  analyzes current product information such as title, description, keywords and uses ChatGPT to provide you with optimized listing content.
